{
  "name": "prelude-ls",

  "author": "George Zahariev <z@georgezahariev.com>",

  "keywords": [
    "prelude",
    "livescript",
    "utility",
    "ls",
    "coffeescript",
    "javascript",
    "library",
    "functional",
    "array",
    "list",
    "object",
    "string"
  ],
  "main": "lib/",
  "files": [
    "lib/",
    "README.md",
    "LICENSE"
  ],
  "homepage": "http://preludels.com",
  "bugs": "https://github.com/gkz/prelude-ls/issues",
  "license": "MIT",
  "engines": {
    "node": ">= 0.8.0"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git://github.com/gkz/prelude-ls.git"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "test": "make test"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "livescript": "^1.6.0",
    "uglify-js": "^3.8.1",
    "mocha": "^7.1.1",
    "browserify": "^16.5.1",
    "sinon": "~8.0.1"
  }
}
